<template>



</template>



<script>
import axios from "axios";
export default {
    name: "AdminView",
    data: function () {
        return {
            list: []
        };
    },
    mounted: function () {
    axios
      .get("http://localhost:8081/api/admin", {withCredentials:'include'})
      .then((res) => {
        this.list = res.data
      })
      .catch((err) =>{ // todo neovlascen pristup
        console.log(err)
      })
   },

}
   
</script>
